wiki.text:
'Versa' or 'VERSA' may refer to:
* VERSA, a sub-brand for NEC's computer products
* Versa (Po), a tributary of the Po which runs through the Province of Pavia in
  northern Italy
* Versa (query language), an RDF query language
* Versa (Tanaro), a tributary of the Tanaro which runs through the Province of
  Asti in northern Italy
* Maruti Versa a multi purpose vehicle (MPV) made by Maruti Udyog Limited and
  sold in India
* Nissan Versa, the North American market name of the Nissan Tiida automobile
  *Optare Versa, a British-built midibus
* VerSA, a vertical situation awareness display by Boeing
